    <title>全系linux VPS两步开启魔改BBR</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/09/21/%E5%85%A8%E7%B3%BBlinux-VPS%E4%B8%A4%E6%AD%A5%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E9%AD%94%E6%94%B9BBR/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/09/21/全系linux-VPS两步开启魔改BBR/</id>
    <published>2018-09-20T18:54:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-09-27T08:29:05.027Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>随着Linux系统内核不断升级，破解版锐速渐渐的跟不上了。BBR以其原生占用小的特点赢得越来越多人的喜爱，魔改版的BBR更是听说非常暴力。这里分享一个找到的魔改BBR脚本，在Ubuntu系统上测试成功。该脚本借鉴了Vicer大佬的脚本，执行两步后最后输出<strong>==Finish！==</strong>则成功。</p><p>Github地址：<a href="https://github.com/xratzh/CBBR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/xratzh/CBBR</a></p><h1 id="Debian-Ubuntu（64位）开启魔改BBR"><a href="#Debian-Ubuntu（64位）开启魔改BBR" class="headerlink" title="Debian/Ubuntu（64位）开启魔改BBR"></a><strong>Debian/Ubuntu（64位）开启魔改BBR</strong></h1><h3 id="Ubuntu14-04需要提前："><a href="#Ubuntu14-04需要提前：" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu14.04需要提前："></a>Ubuntu14.04需要提前：</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install -y software-properties-common</span><br><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository ppa:ubuntu-toolchain-r/<span class="built_in">test</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get -y install g++-4.9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Debian9需要提前："><a href="#Debian9需要提前：" class="headerlink" title="Debian9需要提前："></a>Debian9需要提前：</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget http://snapshot.debian.org/archive/debian/20150123T220434Z/pool/main/o/openssl/libssl1.0.0_1.0.2-1_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">dpkg -i libssl1.0.0_1.0.2-1_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="以下命令Debian-Ubuntu通用"><a href="#以下命令Debian-Ubuntu通用" class="headerlink" title="以下命令Debian/Ubuntu通用"></a>以下命令Debian/Ubuntu通用</h2><h3 id="第一步："><a href="#第一步：" class="headerlink" title="第一步："></a>第一步：</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install -y wget &amp;&amp; wget --no-check-certificate -O D1.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xratzh/CBBR/master/D1.sh &amp;&amp; bash D1.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="之后要求输入Y就会重启"><a href="#之后要求输入Y就会重启" class="headerlink" title="之后要求输入Y就会重启"></a>之后要求输入Y就会重启</h3><h3 id="第二步："><a href="#第二步：" class="headerlink" title="第二步："></a>第二步：</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget --no-check-certificate -O D2.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xratzh/CBBR/master/D2.sh &amp;&amp; bash D2.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>–</p><h1 id="CentOS7开启魔改BBR"><a href="#CentOS7开启魔改BBR" class="headerlink" title="CentOS7开启魔改BBR"></a><strong>CentOS7开启魔改BBR</strong></h1><h3 id="第一步：-1"><a href="#第一步：-1" class="headerlink" title="第一步："></a>第一步：</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y wget &amp;&amp; wget --no-check-certificate -O C71.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xratzh/CBBR/master/C71.sh &amp;&amp; bash C71.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="之后同样会要求输入Y重启"><a href="#之后同样会要求输入Y重启" class="headerlink" title="之后同样会要求输入Y重启"></a>之后同样会要求输入Y重启</h5><h3 id="第二步：-1"><a href="#第二步：-1" class="headerlink" title="第二步："></a>第二步：</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget --no-check-certificate -O C72.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xratzh/CBBR/master/C72.sh &amp;&amp; bash C72.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>–</p><h1 id="CentOS6开启魔改BBR"><a href="#CentOS6开启魔改BBR" class="headerlink" title="CentOS6开启魔改BBR"></a><strong>CentOS6开启魔改BBR</strong></h1><h3 id="第一步：-2"><a href="#第一步：-2" class="headerlink" title="第一步："></a>第一步：</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y wget &amp;&amp; wget --no-check-certificate -O C61.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xratzh/CBBR/master/C61.sh &amp;&amp; bash C61.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="之后输入Y就会重启"><a href="#之后输入Y就会重启" class="headerlink" title="之后输入Y就会重启"></a>之后输入Y就会重启</h5><h3 id="第二步：-2"><a href="#第二步：-2" class="headerlink" title="第二步："></a>第二步：</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget --no-check-certificate -O C62.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xratzh/CBBR/master/C62.sh &amp;&amp; bash C62.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>–</p><p>存在对于其他内核的删除，只保留4.11.8内核<br>为什么不能一键，因为Linux内核在4.0后支持不重启更换，但是CentOS和Debian/Ubuntu很多的内核都是3.X的版本，Debian9和Ubuntu16.04则是4.X的版本。<br>Xratzh压力测试，发现bbr和魔改bbr都开启时会达到最快（个人验证）<br>脚本里加入了对内核的锁定，之后update时不会变动内核。内核统一选择4.11.8版本。</p><p>–</p><h1 id="Ps-本教程转至-厘米天空"><a href="#Ps-本教程转至-厘米天空" class="headerlink" title="Ps: 本教程转至 ==厘米天空=="></a>Ps: <em>本教程转至 ==<a href="https://www.cmsky.com/bbr-powered" target="_blank" rel="noopener">厘米天空</a>==</em></h1>]]></content>
    
